}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== ===Product Key Features=== *[[Qualcomm Atheros]] QCA9888 chipset (802.11abgn/ac 2T2R) *5GHz max 25dBm output power (per chain), 21dBm (aggregate) *802.11ac compliant & backward compatible with 802.11a/n *2x2 MIMO Technology, up to 1733Mbps *Support for 160MHz *MiniPCI Express 1.1 interface *Supports Spatial Multiplexing, Maximal Ratio Combining (MRC), :Cyclic Delay Diversity (CDD), Space Time Block Code (STBC), :Low-Density Parity-Check (LDPC) Codes *Supports 802.11d, e, h, i, k, r, v time stamp, and w standards *Supports Dynamic Frequency Selection (DFS)
